: "screenshot3.png", "id": "424898228825571", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75303838_424898232158904_8057494205377644656_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TvQ0-OfCXUwQ7kNvgEcbsTD&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAoCTlcef4O7PxfYJ5ZNUM9vcKolZ9YBTMK4J8gfusi5w&oe=675C1993"}, {"file_name": "screenshot5.png", "id": "257663129204712", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75422370_257663132538045_3715272386866238300_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Ksd3RirInMgQ7kNvgGxMiDw&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAlHlLAcdLeJU3biTyVuR3uc1YTXSF5YN6ONEzRGWfv2Q&oe=675C2FCA"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "FigureOut VR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Use the given Figures to fill the empty Fields . Use the Touch Controllers or the Game Menu to control the music. \nFull Room-Scale with different zoom stages.\nJust fill all the empty wood blocks with the given figures to advance to the next level.\n\nPlease copy your music files by making a new folder called figureout inside the music folder.\n\nFeatures: \n- 100 Levels\n- Easy to pickup\n- Use your own Music\n- Full Oculus Touch controller support\n- Dark and light background to choose from (B/Y Button)\n- Different scale sizes\n- Two different difficulties\n\nController Mapping:\nA/X Button: Open menu\nB/Y Button: Dark/Light Background\nUse both Grab Buttons to control the camera\nBoth Joysticks:\nUp/Down: Scale scene\nPress: Play/Stop Song\nRight/Left: Next/Previous Song\nPress both Trigger Buttons when a level is solved to quickly advance to the next level", "short_description": "Relaxing little Puzzle Game. Use the given Figures to fill the empty Fields and listen to your Music."}]}, "developer_name": "Daniel Ali", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.privacypolicies.com/live/04e10ea4-a388-4539-a810-86f7c0a95368", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null,